{
  "pages": {
    "start": [
      {
        "storage.clear": {}
      },
      {
        "storage.set": {
          "key": "obedience",
          "value": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "storage.set": {
          "key": "defiance",
          "value": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "storage.set": {
          "key": "favor",
          "value": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "audio.play": {
          "url": "https://cdn.pixabay.com/audio/2024/10/07/audio_5dbdeb2487.mp3",
          "id": "ambience",
          "loops": 0,
          "background": true,
          "volume": 0.4
        }
      },
      {
        "image": {
          "url": "https://cdni.pornpics.com/1280/1/297/14285021/14285021_002_17e5.jpg"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "你跪在冰冷的地板上，面前是维罗妮卡女主人。她的目光既严厉又充满期待。"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“从今天起，你将是我的财产。你不再有名字，直到我赐予你一个。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“现在，告诉我，我该如何称呼你，我的宠物？”"
        }
      },
      {
        "prompt": {
          "var": "slaveName"
        }
      },
      {
        "storage.set": {
          "key": "slaveName",
          "value": "$slaveName"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“很好，<eval>storage.get('slaveName')</eval>。一个不错的名字...暂时用着吧。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "notification.create": {
          "id": "main_rule",
          "label": "首要规则：取悦主人",
          "button": "铭记于心",
          "commands": [
            {
              "say": {
                "label": "你的每一个选择都将被观察和评判。"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "goto": {
          "target": "first_trial"
        }
      }
    ],
    "first_trial": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“你的第一个任务，” 女主人说着，优雅地伸出她穿着高跟鞋的脚。“擦亮我的靴子，直到能映出你的脸。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "choice": {
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "“是，我的女主人。” (立即顺从地开始)",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "eval": {
                    "action": "Storage.set('obedience', Storage.get('obedience') + 2); Storage.set('favor', Storage.get('favor') + 1);"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "say": {
                    "label": "你谦卑地开始工作，每一个动作都小心翼翼。女主人发出一声满意的哼声。"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "goto": {
                    "target": "second_trial_hub"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "犹豫片刻",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "eval": {
                    "action": "Storage.set('defiance', Storage.get('defiance') + 1);"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "say": {
                    "label": "“怎么了？” 她的声音变冷了。“你在质疑我的命令吗？”"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "goto": {
                    "target": "punishment_hesitation"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "punishment_hesitation": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“对于犹豫不决的惩罚...你将在这里跪着反省，直到我满意为止。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "timer": {
          "duration": "15s",
          "style": "text",
          "id": "punishment_timer"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "冰冷的感觉从你的膝盖传来。你学会了不该挑战她的耐心。"
        }
      },
      {
        "goto": {
          "target": "second_trial_hub"
        }
      }
    ],
    "second_trial_hub": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“下一个任务。我需要一杯酒。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "choice": {
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "前往酒窖",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "goto": {
                    "target": "wine_cellar"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "询问女主人的喜好",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "if": {
                    "condition": "Storage.get('favor') > 0",
                    "commands": [
                      {
                        "eval": {
                          "action": "Storage.set('favor', Storage.get('favor') + 1);"
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "say": {
                          "label": "“哦？你竟然想到了这一层。很好。我喜欢来自‘猩红山谷’的年份。”"
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "storage.set": {
                          "key": "knows_preference",
                          "value": true
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "goto": {
                          "target": "wine_cellar"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "elseCommands": [
                      {
                        "say": {
                          "label": "“放肆！谁允许你提问的？去拿就是了！”"
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "goto": {
                          "target": "wine_cellar"
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "wine_cellar": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "酒窖里排列着数百瓶酒。时间紧迫，女主人不喜欢等待。"
        }
      },
      {
        "timer": {
          "id": "wine_timer",
          "duration": "20s",
          "style": "bar",
          "commands": [
            {
              "goto": {
                "target": "ending_failure_slow"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "if": {
          "condition": "Storage.get('knows_preference') === true",
          "commands": [
            {
              "goto": {
                "target": "wine_cellar_knows_preference"
              }
            }
          ],
          "elseCommands": [
            {
              "goto": {
                "target": "wine_cellar_does_not_know"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "wine_cellar_knows_preference": [
      {
        "choice": {
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "寻找‘猩红山谷’",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "timer.remove": {
                    "id": "wine_timer"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "say": {
                    "label": "你迅速找到了那瓶酒，完美地完成了任务。"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "eval": {
                    "action": "Storage.set('obedience', Storage.get('obedience') + 2); Storage.set('favor', Storage.get('favor') + 2);"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "goto": {
                    "target": "final_test_prep"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "wine_cellar_does_not_know": [
      {
        "choice": {
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "随便拿一瓶红酒",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "timer.remove": {
                    "id": "wine_timer"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "say": {
                    "label": "你选了一瓶看起来很昂贵的酒。"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "goto": {
                    "target": "final_test_prep"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "拿一瓶白酒",
              "commands": [
                {
                  "timer.remove": {
                    "id": "wine_timer"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "say": {
                    "label": "你选了一瓶冰镇的白酒。"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "storage.set": {
                    "key": "wrong_wine",
                    "value": true
                  }
                },
                {
                  "goto": {
                    "target": "final_test_prep"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "final_test_prep": [
      {
        "if": {
          "condition": "Storage.get('wrong_wine') === true",
          "commands": [
            {
              "say": {
                "label": "“白酒？你是在侮辱我的品味吗？”女主人的脸阴沉了下来。"
              }
            },
            {
              "eval": {
                "action": "Storage.set('favor', Storage.get('favor') - 2); Storage.set('defiance', Storage.get('defiance') + 1);"
              }
            }
          ],
          "elseCommands": [
            {
              "say": {
                "label": "女主人接过酒杯，满意地抿了一口。"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“现在，是最后的考验了，<eval>Storage.get('slaveName')</eval>。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "goto": {
          "target": "final_test"
        }
      }
    ],
    "final_test": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“你表现得不错...或者说，非常差劲。”她的评价取决于你之前的行为。"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "“看着我，<eval>Storage.get('slaveName')</eval>。告诉我，你学到了什么？”"
        }
      },
      {
        "prompt": {
          "var": "final_answer"
        }
      },
      {
        "if": {
          "condition": "Storage.get('obedience') > Storage.get('defiance') && Storage.get('favor') > 2",
          "commands": [
            {
              "goto": {
                "target": "ending_perfect_pet"
              }
            }
          ],
          "elseCommands": [
            {
              "if": {
                "condition": "Storage.get('defiance') > Storage.get('obedience')",
                "commands": [
                  {
                    "goto": {
                      "target": "ending_defiant_one"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "elseCommands": [
                  {
                    "goto": {
                      "target": "ending_mediocre"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "ending_perfect_pet": [
      {
        "image": {
          "url": "https://cdni.pornpics.com/1280/1/297/14285021/14285021_002_17e5.jpg"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "【完美服从结局】“你学得很快，我的宠物。”女主人微笑着，声音中带着一丝真正的暖意。“你证明了你的价值。从今晚起，你将睡在我的房间里。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "你赢得了她的青睐，成为了她最珍爱的所有物。这是你所能期望的最高荣耀。"
        }
      },
      {
        "end": {}
      }
    ],
    "ending_defiant_one": [
      {
        "image": {
          "url": "https://cdni.pornpics.com/1280/1/297/14285021/14285021_002_17e5.jpg"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "【叛逆顽固结局】“冥顽不灵。”她冷冷地宣判。“看来你需要更多时间来学习最基本的礼仪。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "你被拖入了最深处的地牢。在这里，你将有无尽的时间来思考你的错误，直到你的反抗之心被彻底磨灭。"
        }
      },
      {
        "end": {}
      }
    ],
    "ending_mediocre": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "【平庸之物结局】“不好不坏。你只是个普通的工具，仅此而已。”她挥了挥手，眼中没有丝毫波澜。"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "你被指派去做最乏味的杂务。你没有赢得她的青睐，也没能激起她的怒火。你只是一个被遗忘在角落的影子。"
        }
      },
      {
        "end": {}
      }
    ],
    "ending_failure_slow": [
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "【无能失败结局】“连这点小事都做不好...我没有时间浪费在无能的废物身上。”"
        }
      },
      {
        "say": {
          "label": "你甚至没来得及看清她的动作，就被卫兵架了出去，扔到了庄园之外。你的服务到此结束。"
        }
      },
      {
        "end": {}
      }
    ]
  }
}